# This GitHub repository is a product information and download page.
# Application source, build tooling, tests, local data, and private books stay local.
*

!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!README.md
!SECURITY.md
!THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md

!docs/
docs/*
!docs/USER_AND_AGENT_GUIDE.md
!docs/PUBLIC_RELEASE_AUDIT.md
!docs/images/
docs/images/*
!docs/images/notebooks-bookshelf.png
!docs/images/notebooks-writing-guide.png
!docs/images/notebooks-cover-studio.png

!downloads/
downloads/*
!downloads/Notebooks-Field-Guide.inkbook

# The installer is uploaded as a GitHub Release asset, never committed to Git.
release-assets/
